      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.space3sixty.com/&#34;&gt;Space360&lt;/a&gt; asked me to create a logo animation for a new logo they designed for their client &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.choicetool.com/&#34;&gt;Choice&lt;/a&gt; as part of their marketing package.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Choice is a tool and mold company, so an important aspect of their branding is machines and lasers. To communicate this, Space360 decided to go with an almost completely steel environment, except for a deep red lake that matches their identity&amp;rsquo;s primary color.&lt;/p&gt;

