&lt;h2 id=&#34;revisited-april-2015&#34;&gt;Revisited April 2015&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.onyxcinema.com/&#34;&gt;Onyx Cinema&lt;/a&gt; is an incredible cinematography company. After years of skill and network growth, they decided it was time to re-brand and get a new website. They hired a colleague of mine to design the logo, and she directed them to me for the animation aspect of it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;project-image&#34;&gt;
